 The Middelburg Mall has a jam-packed weekend full of fun activities planned for your entertainment. Aneldie Francis. They are offering a variety of free games and prizes to keep your children busy, like face painting, ring toss, hoop shoot, a photo booth for happy snapping, feed the clown and naughts and crosses.  The staff at Middelburg Mall encourage you to swing by and give their games a try to see if you can win some of their awesome prizes. Zenande Skosana ready to get some popcorn. The Winter Carnival will be taking place for the whole weekend from 09:00 – 18:00. Don’t miss it!         Middelburg police officer arrested during Hawks operation Botshabelo’s last song Five busted for dagga Nabbed cops granted bail  • Save our standby number (072 248 3855) and send us a WhatsApp message with the words “Add me” to be added to our broadcast list. • Like us on Facebook, follow us on Twitter and Instagram. • Subscribe to our YouTube channel. • Click on the link to subscribe to our bi-weekly newsletter via email. Contact our news room on our 24 hr standby number 072 248 3855, or send a mail to our editor tobie@mobserver.co.za